OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1780009385
OL,3,CUS and Iran 'reach tentative agreement
OL,4,Cto extend ceasefire by 60 days'
OL,6,FThe US and Iran have reached a
OL,7,Ftentative agreement to extend a
OL,8,Fceasefire between them by 60 days and
OL,9,Fto launch talks on Tehran's nuclear
OL,10,Fprogramme, according to a US official
OL,11,Fwith knowledge of the talks.
OL,13,FUS President Donald Trump will still
OL,14,Fneed to sign off on the emerging deal,
OL,15,Fthe official, who spoke on the
OL,16,Fcondition of anonymity, told the
OL,17,FAssociated Press on Thursday.
OL,19,FIran has not confirmed any deal has
OL,20,Fbeen struck between the two countries.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/8
