PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1780009385
OL,3,CUS and Iran 'reach tentative agreement
OL,4,Cto extend ceasefire by 60 days'
OL,6,FThe tentative agreement comes as the
OL,7,Ffragile seven-week ceasefire between
OL,8,Fthe US and Iran appeared to be
OL,9,Fwavering, with both sides repeatedly
OL,10,Faccusing each other of violating it in
OL,11,Fthe last few days.
OL,13,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,14,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,15,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,16,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/8
