PN,30503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1780009385
OL,3,CUS and Iran 'reach tentative agreement
OL,4,Cto extend ceasefire by 60 days'
OL,6,FEarlier on Thursday, US Central
OL,7,FCommand said Kuwait had intercepted
OL,8,Fmissiles from Iran on Wednesday night,
OL,9,Fwith military officials calling the
OL,10,Fincident an "egregious ceasefire
OL,11,Fviolation".
OL,13,FIran said it had fired on a US base in
OL,14,Fa Gulf state it did not name in
OL,15,Fretaliation for strikes earlier in the
OL,16,Fweek, making it unclear if the
OL,17,Fmissiles were intended to hit Kuwait.
OL,19,FThe Kuwaiti Foreign Ministry condemned
OL,20,FIran for what it called "blatant
OL,21,Faggression".
OL,26,@rD@MOU|D@YOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/8
