FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1780009385
OL,3,CUS and Iran 'reach tentative agreement
OL,4,Cto extend ceasefire by 60 days'
OL,6,FAmerican forces had shot down four one-
OL,7,Fway attack drones around the Strait of
OL,8,FHormuz and hit a ground-control
OL,9,Fstation in Bandar Abbas that was about
OL,10,Fto launch a fifth, US officials said
OL,11,Fon Wednesday evening.
OL,13,FOn Monday, the US also conducted what
OL,14,Fthe Pentagon called "self-defense"
OL,15,Fstrikes on missile launch sites and
OL,16,Fminelaying boats in southern Iran.
OL,18,FBoth sides have continued to negotiate
OL,19,Fdespite the attacks, with Trump
OL,20,Finsisting his administration was
OL,21,Fmaking headway in the talks.
OL,26,@vD@UOUvD@bO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/8
