FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30505
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1780009385
OL,3,CUS and Iran 'reach tentative agreement
OL,4,Cto extend ceasefire by 60 days'
OL,6,F"Right now I think it looks like
OL,7,F(Iran) just want to make a deal, I
OL,8,Fdon't think they have a choice," Trump
OL,9,Fsaid during a meeting with his cabinet
OL,10,Fon Wednesday.
OL,12,FThe US president wants the Strait of
OL,13,FHormuz to be fully reopened, and for
OL,14,FIran to give up its stockpile of
OL,15,Fhighly enriched uranium.
OL,17,FThe Islamic Republic is looking for
OL,18,Feconomic sanctions to be lifted and
OL,19,Ffrozen assets to be released to aid
OL,20,Fits shattered economy.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30506
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1780009385
OL,3,CUS and Iran 'reach tentative agreement
OL,4,Cto extend ceasefire by 60 days'
OL,6,FAny deal between the countries must
OL,7,Falso include an end to Israel's
OL,8,Fmilitary operations in Lebanon against
OL,9,Fthe Iranian-backed militant group
OL,10,FHezbollah, Iran has insisted.
OL,12,FA US-brokered ceasefire went into
OL,13,Feffect in Lebanon in mid-April, and
OL,14,FLebanese and Israeli military
OL,15,Fofficials are set to hold their first
OL,16,Fsecurity talks Friday in Washington.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
