OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1780009385
OL,3,CUS and Iran 'reach tentative agreement
OL,4,Cto extend ceasefire by 60 days'
OL,6,FIt was reported on Thursday that
OL,7,FIsraeli strikes killed at least 14
OL,8,Fpeople in southern Lebanon, while one
OL,9,Fsoldier was killed in a drone attack
OL,10,Fby Hezbollah in northern Israel.
OL,12,FAt least 3,269 people have been killed
OL,13,Fin Israeli strikes since the start of
OL,14,Fthe conflict, according to Lebanon's
OL,15,FHealth Ministry, with more than 9,800
OL,16,Fwounded.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/8
